    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">- trag#viki#Rename()<br>- Generalized trag#rename#Rename()<br>- Enabled &quot;trace cursor&quot; functionality (mapped to the &lt;c-insert&gt; key).<br>- :Traglw<br>- TRagGitFiles, trag#SetGitFiles(), g:trag_git</td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=10036">trag.vba.gz</a></td>
    <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><b>0.5</b></td>
